de.weltraumschaf.ebnf
Class Token

java.lang.Object
  de.weltraumschaf.ebnf.Token

public class Token
extends Object

Represents a scanned EBNF token with its type, value and position in the source file. A token is a immutable value object.

Author:
Sven Strittmatter
